    {
      "instruction": "<p>Strip your <strong>mint leaves</strong> from their stems and chop them roughly, discard the stems</p><p>Combine your <strong>mayo</strong> and <strong>chopped mint</strong> in a small mixing bowl with a large drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>minty mayo</strong></p><p>Slice your <strong>tomato[es]</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/749.-step-6-x200.jpg",
