    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> patty[ies]</strong>, press down firmly with a spatula and cook for 5 min</p><p>Tip: Cooking for 5? You may need to do this in batches!</p><p>Flip each <strong>patty</strong> and reduce the heat to medium-high and cook for 5 min further until cooked through and charred (no pink meat!)</p><p>Carefully cut the <strong>warmed</strong> <strong>ciabatta[s]</strong> in half</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
