            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>To assemble, layer your <strong>ciabatta base</strong> with a pile of <strong>quick-pickled cucumber</strong>, a <strong>lamb patty</strong>, <strong>sliced tomato </strong>and a generous dollop of<strong> minty mayo</strong>, then top with the <strong>ciabatta lid </strong>– this is your <strong>lamb burger</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> lamb burger </strong>with the <strong>wedges</strong> and any<strong> remaining minty mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
